# apps/api м „мҡ© нҷҳкІҪліҖмҲҳ вҖ” лЈЁнҠё .env.exampleмқ„ м°ёкі н•ҳм—¬ мұ„мҡё кІғ.
# ліё нҢҢмқјмқҖ м»Ён…Ңмқҙл„Ҳ/лЎңм»¬ dev мӢң `dotenv_path`лЎң мӮ¬мҡ©.

PINVI_ENVIRONMENT=development
PINVI_DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://pinvi:pinvi_dev_password@localhost:5432/pinvi
PINVI_DATABASE_POOL_SIZE=10
PINVI_JWT_SECRET_KEY=pinvi-local-jwt-secret-change-me
PINVI_ACCESS_TOKEN_MINUTES=15
PINVI_REFRESH_TOKEN_DAYS=7
PINVI_MCP_JWT_SECRET=pinvi-local-mcp-secret-change-me
PINVI_MCP_TOKEN_DEFAULT_DAYS=30
PINVI_MCP_RATE_LIMIT_PER_MINUTE=60
PINVI_WEB_BASE_URL=http://localhost:12805
# production: PINVI_WEB_BASE_URL=https://pinvi.digitie.mywire.org
PINVI_EMAIL_VERIFICATION_PATH=/verify-email
PINVI_RESEND_API_KEY=
PINVI_RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=Pinvi <noreply@send.pinvi.local>
PINVI_RESEND_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
# кё°ліё false(м•Ҳм „). лЎңм»¬м—җм„ң м„ңлӘ… м—Ҷмқҙ н…ҢмҠӨнҠён•  л•Ңл§Ң trueлЎң. мҡҙмҳҒ/мҠӨн…Ңмқҙм§•мқҖ false мң м§Җ.
PINVI_RESEND_WEBHOOK_ALLOW_UNSIGNED=false
PINVI_CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=["http://localhost:12805","http://127.0.0.1:12805"]
# production: PINVI_CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=["https://pinvi.digitie.mywire.org"]
# RustFS (S3 нҳёнҷҳ к°қмІҙ м ҖмһҘмҶҢ) вҖ” лЎңм»¬ кіөмң  кё°ліёк°’мқҖ kor-travel-geo кё°мӨҖ.
PINVI_RUSTFS_ENDPOINT_URL=http://localhost:12101
PINVI_RUSTFS_PUBLIC_ENDPOINT_URL=http://127.0.0.1:12101
PINVI_RUSTFS_BUCKET=pinvi-media
PINVI_RUSTFS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=rustfsadmin
PINVI_RUSTFS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=rustfsadmin
PINVI_RUSTFS_PRESIGNED_URL_EXPIRES_SECONDS=900
PINVI_RUSTFS_MAX_UPLOAD_BYTES=10485760
PINVI_RUSTFS_ALLOWED_CONTENT_TYPES=["image/jpeg","image/png","image/webp","image/gif","video/mp4","application/pdf"]
PINVI_RUSTFS_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=
# kor-travel-map лҸ…лҰҪ н”„лЎңк·ёлһЁ (м§ҖлҸ„ feature OpenAPI HTTP, ADR-026/027)
PINVI_KOR_TRAVEL_MAP_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:12701
# admin feature change(/v1/admin/features*)лҸ„ к°ҷмқҖ нҳёмҠӨнҠё :12701
PINVI_KOR_TRAVEL_MAP_ADMIN_BASE_URL=http://localhost:12701
# мҡҙмҳҒ мқёмҰқмқҖ мқён”„лқј кі„мёө. м„Өм • мӢң X-Kor-Travel-Map-Service-Token н—ӨлҚ”лЎң м „лӢ¬.
PINVI_KOR_TRAVEL_MAP_SERVICE_TOKEN=
# admin-path м „мҡ© нҶ нҒ°(лҜём„Өм • мӢң мң„ SERVICE_TOKEN fallback). В§7 admin мқёмҰқ н•©мқҳ лҢҖкё°.
PINVI_KOR_TRAVEL_MAP_ADMIN_SERVICE_TOKEN=
PINVI_KOR_TRAVEL_MAP_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=5
PINVI_KOR_TRAVEL_MAP_MAX_ATTEMPTS=3
PINVI_KOR_TRAVEL_MAP_BATCH_CHUNK_SIZE=200

PINVI_KOR_TRAVEL_GEO_BASE_URL=http://localhost:12501
PINVI_KOR_TRAVEL_GEO_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=5
PINVI_KOR_TRAVEL_GEO_MAX_ATTEMPTS=3

PINVI_GEOFENCE_TRUSTED_PROXY_HEADER=X-Pinvi-Geofence-Proxy
PINVI_GEOFENCE_TRUSTED_PROXY_SECRET=
PINVI_GEOFENCE_TRUSTED_PROXY_CIDRS=[]
PINVI_GEOFENCE_MTLS_VERIFIED_HEADER=
PINVI_GEOFENCE_MTLS_VERIFIED_VALUE=SUCCESS
PINVI_WS_CLIENT_RATE_PER_SECOND=5
PINVI_WS_CLIENT_RATE_PER_MINUTE=60
PINVI_WS_RATE_LIMIT_CLOSE_GRACE_SECONDS=30
PINVI_WS_MAX_CONNECTIONS_PER_TRIP=10
PINVI_WS_MAX_CONNECTIONS_TOTAL=200
PINVI_WS_SEND_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=2
PINVI_PROMETHEUS_METRICS_ENABLED=true
PINVI_PROMETHEUS_METRICS_PATH=/metrics
PINVI_PROMETHEUS_EXCLUDE_PATHS=["/health","/health/db","/metrics"]
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_ENABLED=true
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_BACKEND=auto
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_FAIL_OPEN=false
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_SECONDS=60
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_PUBLIC_PER_MINUTE=60
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_AUTHENTICATED_PER_MINUTE=60
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_AUTH_PER_MINUTE=5
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_OAUTH_PER_MINUTE=10
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_STORAGE_UPLOAD_PER_MINUTE=30
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_FEATURE_SEARCH_PER_MINUTE=60
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_TRIP_EXPORT_PER_MINUTE=20
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_SHARED_TOKEN_PER_MINUTE=60
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_CLIENT_IP_HEADER=
PINVI_RATE_LIMIT_BYPASS_PATHS=["/health","/health/db","/metrics","/docs","/redoc","/openapi.json"]
PINVI_OAUTH_CALLBACK_BASE_URL=http://localhost:12801
# production: PINVI_OAUTH_CALLBACK_BASE_URL=https://pinviapi.digitie.mywire.org

PINVI_BACKUP_DIR=.tmp/backups
PINVI_BACKUP_SCRIPT_PATH=scripts/backup-db.sh
PINVI_RESTORE_SCRIPT_PATH=scripts/restore-db.sh
PINVI_RESTORE_HOTSWAP_SCRIPT_PATH=scripts/restore-hotswap.sh
PINVI_BACKUP_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=900
PINVI_RESTORE_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=3600
PINVI_BACKUP_SCHEMA=app
PINVI_RESTORE_DATABASE_URL=
PINVI_RESTORE_HOTSWAP_EXECUTE=0
PINVI_RESTORE_DRAIN_COMMAND=
PINVI_RESTORE_ALLOW_NO_DRAIN=0
PINVI_RESTORE_APP_ROLE=
